            <text>
                <body>
                    <div xml:lang="nl" type="original">

<p xml:id="p.orig.1" n="1"><pb f="1r" n="1" xml:id="pb-original-1r-1" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1"/></p>

<p xml:id="p.orig.2" n="2">Mijnheer,</p><lb n="1*" xml:id="l-1s"/>

<p xml:id="p.orig.3" n="3">Of ik Zaturdag a.s. kan komen schilderen <lb n="2" xml:id="l-2"/>weet ik niet zeker<c type="kp">.</c>– Omdat ik een paar studies aan <lb n="3" xml:id="l-3"/>’t maken ben hier – van het aardappelzetten<ptr target="#note-t-1"/> – <lb n="4" xml:id="l-4"/>waar ik dien dag in kwestie welligt aan zal moeten <lb n="5" xml:id="l-5"/>blijven werken.</p><lb n="6" xml:id="l-6"/>

<p rend="indent" xml:id="p.orig.4" n="4">Doch indien niet Zaturdag dan kom ik toch – <lb n="7" xml:id="l-7"/>tenzij in geval van tegenberigt uwerzijds – <lb n="8" xml:id="l-8"/>Maandag.</p>
<space unit="lines" quantity="1"/><lb n="9" xml:id="l-9"/>

<p xml:id="p.orig.5" n="5">b. à v.</p><lb n="10" xml:id="l-10"/>

<p xml:id="p.orig.6" n="6">Vincent</p>
<space unit="lines" quantity="1"/><figure facs="zone-sketch-1" n="A"/>
<space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
    
<p xml:id="p.orig.7" n="7"><pb f="1v" n="1" xml:id="pb-orig-1v-2" facs="#zone-pb-1v-2"/></p>
</div>

                    <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                        
<p xml:id="p.trans.1" n="1"><pb f="1r" n="1" xml:id="pb-trans-1r-1" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1"/></p>
<p xml:id="p.trans.2" n="2">Dear <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_475">Sir</rs>,</p>
<p xml:id="p.trans.3" n="3">I’m not sure whether I can come and paint next Saturday. Because I’m making a couple of studies here — of the potato planting<ptr target="#note-t-1"/> — on which I may possibly have to continue to work on the day in question.</p>
<p rend="indent" xml:id="p.trans.4" n="4">But if not Saturday, I’ll come anyway — unless I hear from you to the contrary — on Monday.</p><space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
<p xml:id="p.trans.5" n="5">Yours truly,</p>
<p xml:id="p.trans.6" n="6">Vincent</p><space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
<p xml:id="p.trans.7" n="7"><figure facs="zone-sketch-1" n="A"/></p>
<p xml:id="p.trans.8" n="8"><pb f="1v" n="1" xml:id="pb-trans-1v-2" facs="#zone-pb-1v-2"/></p>
                    </div>
